title: AMD expands midrange FPGA offerings with Kintex UltraScale+ Gen 2 family
description:
AMD engineered the Kintex UltraScale+ Gen 2 FPGAs to meet the increasingly complex system requirements across industrial and medical markets.

The post AMD expands midrange FPGA offerings with Kintex UltraScale+ Gen 2 family appeared first on The Robot Report.
